You can also separate out the non-disposable part into its own sequence and communicate with it via subjects:

```java
Subject<T> input = PublishSubject.create();
Subject<R> output = PublishSubject.create();

// the non-disposable sequence of transformations
input
  .flatMap(v -> operation1())
  .flatMap(w -> operation2())
  .subscribe(output);

// prepare handling the output of the non-disposable part
